687
00:45:18,749 --> 00:45:20,984
If you have a misunderstanding
about my dad,

688
00:45:22,386 --> 00:45:23,887
I'll explain everything.

689
00:45:26,990 --> 00:45:28,225
The truth is

690
00:45:29,193 --> 00:45:30,761
my dad...

