00:51:37,227 --> 00:51:38,428
The door closed.

767
00:51:38,795 --> 00:51:39,930
What do we do?

768
00:51:39,996 --> 00:51:41,331
Don't worry.

769
00:51:42,732 --> 00:51:44,534
I need to get out of here too.

770
00:51:45,368 --> 00:51:46,937
